snippet.textDisplay: Sam and Colby, my name is Saed Lopez and I just have to say that your videos have changed my life and affected my mind in a way that it's draining my energy and I can't even relax. For the past two days, I've been watching your biggest most insane and scariest adventures like the witches forest, Langham hotel and others as well. I want to tell you a story that my father experienced himself onetime with his mother. when my father was at the age of 25 to 30 he was really involved growing up at my grandmother's church and my father is a man of faith and believes in God almighty. short story my father had to take my grandmother to a house that was possessed by a girl who had killed her family in her house. my grandmother was trained to handle this situation so she had to meet up with a couple of church people in this house to cleanse and banish this demon that had possessed a 15 year, old girl. short story my father as soon as he parked his car in front of the girl house, my father could sense an evil that was so dark, that all his life he would never had thought that exited, at the entrance of the house there was the smell of burning and death that he could literally not pass through the gate of the house so my father had to unfortanelly stay outside while his mother has to face something as evil as this.  my father told me that my grandmother went through hours and hours preaching and trying to banish this demon that possessed this girl, they used holy water, they said multiple things to banish this demon and they did, my grandmother was touched by this girl and thank the Lord the demon did not transfer to her because she was trained to handle these situations and her faith was strong, unfortunately, because of the touch her energy made her really exhausted and tired and after 5 to 7 hours of having to go through that whole process she had slept 3 days straight without eating or drinking because that's how much this process affected her. I'm telling you something right now and I mean this and I wish you guys the best luck and I'm praying for you because movies are nothing and everyone knows that but you never ever want to experience or see a person that is possessed or been touched by a demon or experienced a poltragize. Sam, Colby, Jake and Corey please be careful sam I understand that you want to find out how the spirit world works and find also if there something after the afterlife.  but if you take this too far I'm telling you this right now you will be scared and not yourself for the rest of your life. because of me watching your channel for 3 days straight, today December 18th, 2019 I have not slept at all in more than just 10 minutes I went to bed at 3:30am EST and its 5:51am now and all im repeating in my mind is poltragized and honestly, I'm scared to sleep and I'm afraid of the dark and I've not been afraid of the dark since I was 6. I share the same experience as Corey unfortanelly. in 2006 I was 6 years old and I used to live in Puerto Rico up in a hill but we call it halda which is a hill in Spanish and up the hill my aunt lived in a house wherein front of the house there was a light poll shinning light in just one area. when I was heading down the hill at night to go to my house the street pole was blinking insanely fast and it turned off for like one second and when it turned on I saw a shadow that was rising from the ground and it was exactly what Corey describes a shadow man and after that, I started crying and begging it to go away and leave me and I crouched in my knees and I started praying and I begged the Lord to take it away and when i open my eyes the shadow was gone. I just remember after that running straight through that light and never looking back and I got home and I was traumatized. I had never played ouija board in my life but do I know their evil that can be caused without playing ouija board yes. These stories are not BS i really mean all of this and these are true events that my father went through and me too. if your given signs from rituals of things happening just end it there do not proceed further cuz I'm telling you right now YOU WILL REGRET IT!!!. You guys are amazing people and hilarious and funny, fun and energetic I've seen you guys in vine and you guys are awesome but ask yourselves and this goes for the whole squad, is this something that you want to proceed doing and will it end up affecting one of you in A TRAUMATIC WAY FOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE.
